Once per turn: You can discard 1 "Heroic" card; Special Summon 1 "Heroic" monster from your Deck, and if you do, change this card to Defense Position. If you activate this effect, you cannot Special Summon any monsters for the rest of this turn, except "Heroic" monsters. When you take damage from an attack or a card effect while this card is in your Graveyard: You can Special Summon this card from the Graveyard in Attack Position. You can only use this effect of "Heroic Challenger - Thousand Blades" once per turn.
